== *Interests*

His research interests mainly focus on large-scale data management and data mining:
- Graph data analytics: dense subgraph discovery/search, (shortest) path query, motif analysis and graphlet counting, graph learning.
- AI/LLM+DB: text2sql, dataset search, vector search, table reconstruction.
- Traffic data mining: trajectory outlier detection, traffic trajectory search.

